@ twoel

You didn't add an correct meta number in txt file, without that it is not possible to activate map 8.45

I used this Meta text   ; Western_Europe_1GB_845_2666
0C 7B B3 EA E1 7C 24 E5 4E A4 68 26 7A 65 31 9E Western_Europe_1GB-140.meta
and it works on my SE X1

To install this use:
http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/4924240/tomtom_Easy_Activator.zip

Remember to add the line provided by Tolare into the meta.txt file.
